{"type": "article", "id": 28664, "title": "Dior 创意总监将来自 Valentino ，以及，G-Star 春夏款墨镜不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-24T11:54:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 8238, "name": "墨镜"}, {"id": 22961, "name": "粉色"}, {"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 7721, "name": "滑板"}, {"id": 10433, "name": "L’Oreal"}, {"id": 1549, "name": "Kering"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 29382, "name": "Club 75"}, {"id": 4060, "name": "Macy’s"}, {"id": 3289, "name": "梅西百货"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 6839, "name": "Christian Dior"}, {"id": 19214, "name": "G-Star"}, {"id": 22545, "name": "Dries Van Noten"}, {"id": 29383, "name": "Sandro"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170455dAGW2OSNLMaz39ZD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/dior-raf-to-tap-valentinos-maria-grazia-chiuri-10467830/\"><b>Dior 创意总监确定，来自 Valentino</b></a> ｜据 WWD 报道，知情人士透露 Christian Dior 创意总监最终确定人选，来自 Valentino 的意大利设计师 Maria Grazia Chiuri ，若消息属实她将是 Dior 史上首个女性创意总监。据悉，Chiuri 为 Dior 设计的首次作品将在这个秋季发布，即 2017 年春夏的成衣系列。周三她刚刚与搭档 Pierpaolo Piccioli 合作在巴黎发布 Valentino 的 2017 春夏男装系列。对此，Dior 方面拒绝评论。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Macy-s-CEO-Terry-Lundgren-to-be-succeeded-in-2017,706846.html\"><b>梅西百货 13 年任期的 CEO 将离职</b></a>｜梅西百货（Macy’s）周四宣布总裁 Jeff Gennette 将担任公司首席执政官，接替现任 CEO 兼主席 Terry Lundgren 。2017 年一季度开始交接。Gennette 于 1983 年加入梅西，至今 33 年。同时他将加入梅西董事会，即刻生效。而 Lundgren 则从 2003 年起担任 CEO。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/fashion/francesco-smalto-names-eric-bergere-creative-director-10468562/\"><b>Francesco Smalto 任命新创意总监</b></a>｜Eric Bergère 将从七月开始担任老牌男装品牌 Francesco Smalto 创意总监，过去三十年他曾在 Hermès、Lanvin 和 Inès de la Fressange 担任创意总监的职位，并拥有自己的品牌。Francesco Smalto 1962 年在巴黎建立自己的同名男装品牌，2015 年逝世。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Francois-Henri-Pinault-denies-Puma-is-up-for-sale,706971.html\"><b>开云 CEO 否认将出售 Puma</b></a>｜奢侈品集团开云（Kering）的 CEO François-Henri Pinault，近日在接受金融时报采访时表示，短期内并未有出售旗下 Puma 的打算。此前一些分析师确信 Puma 可能被出售但不会早于 2017 年。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/L-Oreal-USA-moves-corporate-headquarters-to-Hudson-Yards,706976.html\"><b>欧莱雅美国总部迁新址</b></a>｜欧莱雅集团（L’Oréal）美国总部近日迁至哈德逊园区（Hudson Yards ）新址，结束位于曼哈顿中城 60 年的历史。新总部大楼有 10 层，占据 40 万平方英尺。此前 Coach 也于五月搬进 Hudson Yards。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>G-Star RAW 发布 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/g-star-raw-2016-spring-summer-sunglasses-lookbook\">2016 年春夏眼镜系列 lookbook</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170436eDpSVIG6QuxLK4i0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170437P3vsXieE9zfYwcBt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170437dDgBRuS7cskvIZK3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170438NZdmF1a2cDb6sS0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170438fhXZtJVen4Bj8lD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170439JRc0NmS43lVIjyQY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/paris/dries-van-noten/review/\">Dries Van Noten 2017 春夏男装系列不错</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170439iGM70anUxFLSp9K4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170440sjUiXAH81t0SoulQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021704406BfYmndTRIxCgyuJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170441YmCnjv3XsH5VapTu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170441fHJeFCrTI1RbYd3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170442x8aK0G3NU4X9klTf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021704428DPaMgvCyGqmQuwL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>简约的法国品牌 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/paris/sandro/review/\">Sandro 2017 男士春夏系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170443Evbt1ZUiCnQxoNur.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170443dzSmJkFRqI3X5B0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170444socHYX3ZRdOaErgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021704446Em1vBxu9ztnOIZs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\